{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775885855339,"sessionID":"ses_284f4b4efffeVqGVcG7anw0B3b","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0baa010011VpvsVRK1zFGzW","messageID":"msg_d7b0b83a9001Y76095uCdNb8rR","sessionID":"ses_284f4b4efffeVqGVcG7anw0B3b","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-6ab20793d55343dc9f33a7783e6626f0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/design.md","offset":1,"limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) |\n8: | Module | `manifests` |\n9: | Language | YAML |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: Define Kubernetes RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, Role/ClusterRole, RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding) for AgentCube components to enable secure, least-privilege access to Kubernetes API resources. Router uses namespace-scoped Role for Secret management; WorkloadManager uses cluster-wide ClusterRole for sandbox lifecycle management and CRD operations.\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Architecture\n18: \n19: ### High-Level Architecture\n20: \n21: ```\n22: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n23: │                         RBAC Architecture                                    │\n24: │                     AgentCube Components                                     │\n25: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n26: │                                                                              │\n27: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n28: │  │                    Router RBAC (Namespace-scoped)                     │   │\n29: │  ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤   │\n30: │  │                                                                       │   │\n31: │  │   ┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐                      │   │\n32: │  │   │ ServiceAccount  │──────│ RoleBinding     │                      │   │\n33: │  │   │ (namespace)     │      │ (namespace)     │                      │   │\n34: │  │   └─────────────────┘      └─────────────────┘                      │   │\n35: │  │                                  │                                   │   │\n36: │  │                                  ▼                                   │   │\n37: │  │                          ┌─────────────────┐                        │   │\n38: │  │                          │ Role            │                        │   │\n39: │  │                          │ (secrets only)  │                        │   │\n40: │  │                          └─────────────────┘                        │   │\n41: │  │                                                                       │   │\n42: │  │   Scope: {{ .Release.Namespace }}                                     │   │\n43: │  │   Permissions: secrets (get/list/watch/create/update/patch/delete)   │   │\n44: │  │   Conditional: router.rbac.create=true                                │   │\n45: │  │                                                                       │   │\n46: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n47: │                                                                              │\n48: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n49: │  │              WorkloadManager RBAC (Cluster-wide)                      │   │\n50: │  ├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤   │\n51: │  │                                                                       │   │\n52: │  │   ┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────────┐                  │   │\n53: │  │   │ ServiceAccount  │──────│ ClusterRoleBinding  │                  │   │\n54: │  │   │ (namespace)     │      │ (cluster-wide)      │                  │   │\n55: │  │   └─────────────────┘      └─────────────────────┘                  │   │\n56: │  │                                  │                                   │   │\n57: │  │                                  ▼                                   │   │\n58: │  │                          ┌─────────────────────┐                    │   │\n59: │  │                          │ ClusterRole         │                    │   │\n60: │  │                          │ (CRDs, Pods,        │                    │   │\n61: │  │                          │  Secrets,           │                    │   │\n62: │  │                          │  TokenReviews)      │                    │   │\n63: │  │                          └─────────────────────┘                    │   │\n64: │  │                                                                       │   │\n65: │  │   Scope: Cluster-wide                                                 │   │\n66: │  │   Permissions:                                                        │   │\n67: │  │     - agents.x-k8s.io: sandboxes                                      │   │\n68: │  │     - extensions.agents.x-k8s.io: sandboxclaims, templates, warmpools │   │\n69: │  │     - runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh: codeinterpreters, agentruntimes   │   │\n70: │  │     - core: pods, secrets                                             │   │\n71: │  │     - authentication.k8s.io: tokenreviews                             │   │\n72: │  │                                                                       │   │\n73: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n74: │                                                                              │\n75: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### RBAC Permission Model\n79: \n80: ```\n81: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n82: │                      Permission Flow Diagram                                  │\n83: ├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n84: │                                                                              │\n85: │   User/External ──────▶ Router ──────▶ Secrets (namespace-scoped)           │\n86: │         │                  │                                                │\n87: │         │                  │         ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │\n88: │         │                  │         │ Role: secrets                    │   │\n89: │         │                  │         │ Verbs: get,list,watch,           │   │\n90: │         │                  │         │        create,update,patch,delete│   │\n91: │         │                  │         └──────────────────────────────────┘   │\n92: │         │                  │                                                │\n93: │         ▼                  ▼                                                │\n94: │                                                                              │\n95: │   Router ──────▶ WorkloadManager ──────▶ Kubernetes API                    │\n96: │         │                  │                                                │\n97: │         │                  │         ┌──────────────────────────────────┐   │\n98: │         │                  │         │ ClusterRole:                     │   │\n99: │         │                  │         │ - Sandboxes (full CRUD)          │   │\n100: │         │                  │         │ - CodeInterpreters (full CRUD)   │   │\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 599. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) |\n| Module | `manifests` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\nDefine Kubernetes RBAC resources (ServiceAccount, Role/ClusterRole, RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding) for AgentCube components to enable secure, least-privilege access to Kubernetes API resources. Router uses namespace-scoped Role for Secret management; WorkloadManager uses cluster-wide ClusterRole for sandbox lifecycle management and CRD operations.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Architecture\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/design.md","time":{"start":1775885855324,"end":1775885855336}}}}
