{"type":"text","timestamp":1775885862756,"sessionID":"ses_284f4b4efffeVqGVcG7anw0B3b","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0bb4ea0019kJzo54rOtKiXM","messageID":"msg_d7b0baa9a0014f38bkftCKvMs9","sessionID":"ses_284f4b4efffeVqGVcG7anw0B3b","type":"text","text":"## AR-031 — RBAC 配置 Summary\n\n**Completed (30% - Phases 1-3):**\n- Router RBAC: ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding (namespace-scoped, secrets access)\n- WorkloadManager RBAC: ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding (cluster-scoped for CRDs, pods, secrets, TokenReviews)\n- Deployment Integration: serviceAccountName wired into Router and WorkloadManager deployments\n- values.yaml defaults added (`router.rbac.create: false`, `router.serviceAccountName: \"\"`)\n\n**Deferred (Phases 4-8):**\n- Permission Validation (T4.1-T4.5)\n- Helm Chart Validation Tests (T5.1-T5.5)\n- Kubernetes API Validation Tests (T6.1-T6.3)\n- Permission Matrix Tests (T7.1-T7.8) - requires deployed cluster\n- Security Audit Tests (T8.1-T8.5)","time":{"start":1775885862755,"end":1775885862755}}}
